1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/dnezekiel13/finance_reports.git
   cd finance_reports


2.Install Dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

PROVIDER=openrouter
MODEL=mistralai/mixtral-8x7b-instruct
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
